{"tid":517460,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Nokia 9或具備由LG生產的5.5吋OLED顯示屏","createTime":"2018-01-02T10:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T17:45:45.000Z","uid":47132,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"73415277ce5f5a88a66b4f0408ab17cd9714c43d","tid":517460,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1970000/1974994/20Dec2017_Morris_3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1970000%2F1974994%2F20Dec2017_Morris_3_600.jpg&h=66777861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旗艦手機Nokia 8與中階手機Nokia 6相繼推出後，諾基亞支持者的目光便落在Nokia 9身上。作為該公司的最新旗艦手機，其部分規格早前已從聯邦通信委員會的文件流出。Nokia 9或具備由LG生產的5.5吋OLED顯示屏，比Nokia 8的IPS LCD顯示屏更佳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據文件透露，該手機配備Snapdragon 835處理器、電池容量達3,250mAh及128GB容量，後置相機分別有1,200萬像素和1,300萬像素雙鏡頭，前置相機鏡頭具500萬像素，並運行最新的Android 8.0 Oreo作業系統。"},{"pid":"3ed8e583866b1bb4e03a5089f499fef95728e7af","tid":517460,"uid":34348,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:34:32.000Z","msg":"LG OLED<br />\n咁可以blacklist定<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056a9eaeaef3f8381c2aef85f2a73edfe5e063e2","tid":517460,"uid":51932,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3ed8e583866b1bb4e03a5089f499fef95728e7af","tid":517460,"uid":34348,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:34:32.000Z","msg":"LG OLED<br />\n咁可以blacklist定<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"自己都搞唔掂，賣俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0bf0e17c67d179267c8cb5013865129989230c","tid":517460,"uid":68094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"139f59c269e49e1dd89a991d5c67cbe6ebadd1e6","tid":517460,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":1